message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. With its advanced features and unparalleled quality, it's not just a purchase but an investment in excellence. Considering its value and the benefits it offers, I propose a price of $12000 for this product. This price reflects the high standards we maintain and the unique value it provides. I believe it represents a fair deal for both of us. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing further or if you have any questions.
